Steps: ---
1. Open Sql Server Management Studio.
2. Connect Database with credentials And Start "SQL Server Agent" (if not started).
3. Create a Folder where you want to save backup.
4. Go to Management and expend.
5. Right Click on "Maintenance Plans" -> click on "Maintenance Plan Wizad".
6. Flow the Process shown in video.

Video URL : https://chittranjanmahto.blogspot.com/2019/08/sql-server-tutorial-1-how-to-automate.html
